        <definition>bt_gatt_attr_read_func_t bt_gatt_attr::read</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>read</name>
        <qualifiedname>bt_gatt_attr::read</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Attribute Value read method. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Readable Attributes must implement this method.</para>
<para>Must be NULL if the attribute is not readable.</para>
<para>The behavior of this method is determined by the Attribute Type.</para>
<para>See <ref refid="group__bt__gatt_1ga4eb3ccdabe11fc510ee8d41c4d2ee0cb" kindref="member">bt_gatt_attr_read_func_t</ref>. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
