        <definition>bt_gatt_attr_write_func_t bt_gatt_attr::write</definition>
        <argsstring></argsstring>
        <name>write</name>
        <qualifiedname>bt_gatt_attr::write</qualifiedname>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Attribute Value write method. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Writeable Attributes must implement this method.</para>
<para>Must be NULL if the attribute is not writable.</para>
<para>The behavior of this method is determined by the Attribute Type.</para>
<para>See <ref refid="group__bt__gatt_1ga7c0ac4fb5111ab9af7af347576be8d9b" kindref="member">bt_gatt_attr_write_func_t</ref>. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
