        <briefdescription>
<para>Attribute Handle. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>The Attribute Handle is an index corresponding to a specific Attribute in the ATT database.</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Use <ref refid="group__bt__gatt__server_1ga2d51136ea1bd6cdb50900639506fd9f7" kindref="member">bt_gatt_attr_get_handle()</ref> for attributes in the local ATT database. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
