        <bitfield> 15</bitfield>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Attribute Permissions. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Bit field of <ref refid="group__bt__gatt_1ga96e57500d2340a45badb23701cc43833" kindref="member">bt_gatt_perm</ref>.</para>
<para>The permissions are security requirements that must be satisfied before calling <ref refid="structbt__gatt__attr_1a074abc719494ca35997a452f526e7ecc" kindref="member">read()</ref> or <ref refid="structbt__gatt__attr_1a1ecd78536067f4bded506e0daccefd35" kindref="member">write()</ref>. </para>
