    <briefdescription>
<para>GATT Attribute. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This type primarily represents an ATT Attribute that may be an entry in the local ATT database. The objects of this type must be part of an array that forms a GATT service.</para>
<para>While the formed GATT service is registered with the local GATT server, pointers to this type can typically be given to GATT server APIs, like <ref refid="group__bt__gatt__server_1ga74ee552864c563aa5bc939f37395c14a" kindref="member">bt_gatt_notify()</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
